 $$N=-\frac{X_\varphi\wedge X_\theta}{2+\cos(\varphi)}
 =\begin{pmatrix}\sin(\varphi)\cos(\theta)\\ \sin(\varphi)\sin(\theta)\\ -\cos (\varphi)\end{pmatrix}
 \wedge \begin{pmatrix}-\sin(\theta)\\ \cos(\theta)\\ 0\end{pmatrix}
 =\begin{pmatrix}
